title: Masters of Horror Composers Collection 2 (horror ost's)
description:
Another Collection of some of the best horror soundtracks
by some amazing composers such as 

Carlo Maria Cordio - Rosso Sangue 
Claudio Simonetti - Demoni
Daemonia - Live... or Dead
Ennio Morricone - Gothic Dramas
Fabio Frizzi - the Beyond
Goblin - Non Ho Sonno
Keith Emerson - Inferno
Mark Isham - The Black Dhahlia
